    "description": "Castle Siege is a multiplayer 1v1 tower defense and offense game, set in a stylized medieval world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712290/extras/45f15d2dd14d21bd6009c4e956bed47f.poster.avif?t=1689274510\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712290/extras/45f15d2dd14d21bd6009c4e956bed47f.webm?t=1689274510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712290/extras/45f15d2dd14d21bd6009c4e956bed47f.mp4?t=1689274510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712290/extras/13f67807db7973ba084669756e625f7d.avif?t=1689274510\" width=600 height=125 /></span><br>One player attacks, and the other defends. The attacker can buy units and send them out to destroy the castle. The defender can place turrets along the path to stop the units.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712290/extras/dd4f5dbb9d4e4f0619dfa7878ad4f3c7.poster.avif?t=1689274510\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712290/extras/dd4f5dbb9d4e4f0619dfa7878ad4f3c7.webm?t=1689274510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712290/extras/dd4f5dbb9d4e4f0619dfa7878ad4f3c7.mp4?t=1689274510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Upgrade your units or turrets to give them special traits like lifesteal, health regeneration or extra damage.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712290/extras/7b9d3457146bd0612e3614f0ef1a30d3.avif?t=1689274510\" width=510 height=482 /></span><br><br>Buy magic spell cards to inflict damage on your opponent, or to buff your own troops.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712290/extras/8c4920c626a7a769d5f9af621c0ccad8.poster.avif?t=1689274510\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712290/extras/8c4920c626a7a769d5f9af621c0ccad8.webm?t=1689274510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712290/extras/8c4920c626a7a769d5f9af621c0ccad8.mp4?t=1689274510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712290/extras/98ac619c732ded586584d149d962ab7f.avif?t=1689274510\" width=600 height=125 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Tactical tower defense gameplay.<br></li><li> Strategic tower offense gameplay.<br></li><li> Use spell cards to gain an upper hand.<br></li><li> Level up by killing units or turrets.<br></li><li> Gain stronger spells and upgrades.<br></li><li> Customize your castle flag using colors and symbols.</li></ul>",
